      "date": "2018-10-16 10:47:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHello James.\nWhat Test-Parameters should be set to have ha.sh run in the automation with proper options pass to the script?\nResults show that parameters are missing:\n/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/ha.sh: 13:13:39 1539263619: -c is mandatory\n\nPlease advice.\nThanks.",
